		<RichText x="738" y="255" width="429" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">发生器叠加电锯部件，产生力场屏障平推出去，接触持续造成<span color="#b9b9b9">30%,15%,7.5%,<br/>3%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="479" width="399" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">游离的电锯部件追踪玩家，接触造成<span color="#b9b9b9">50%,25%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="703" width="437" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">发生器游离出两个<span textDecoration="underline">电锯部件</span><span>，自己进入隐蔽状态，驱散所有元素附着，</span><span color="#ffbfbf">全抗性提升50%</span><span>，每个部件继承10%的发生器生命值，状态持续10-20s。在本体上进行</span><span color="#99ff86">激化反应</span><span>或其使被</span><span color="#4cffa5">「真识波」</span><span>命中，可解除该状态并使其瘫痪。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="991" width="410" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">隐蔽状态下，若击破任意一个电锯部件，则会使发生器进入<span textDecoration="underline">修复部件</span><span>状态。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/元能构装体%B7力场发生器.assets/Image_14.png')" x="719" y="169">
		</BitmapImage>
