		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#34529e" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#34529e">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1068" width="435" height="78" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">电锯部件：12盾量的10%生命值盾，继承召唤者的生命值上限，其他属性相同；每秒消耗0.2直至损毁。<br/>修复中的电锯部件：<span color="#99ff85">4草</span><span>盾，1次</span><span color="#ffacff">雷元素</span><span>攻击即可，其他元素只反应不消耗。击破后瘫痪构装体。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="63" y="533" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="40" fontStyle="italic" fontWeight="normal" color="#c4c6fa" width="354" height="43" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="40" fontStyle="italic" color="#c4c6fa">砂原王都的建造者</p>
			</content>
